data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom home located in Juniata. This property greets you with a well-manicured garden and large patio perfect for outdoor entertaining. As you move through this property you will be wowed by the meticulous details, and professionally done upgrades. Stepping inside you'll immediately notice the hardwood floors throughout, enhancing the bright and airy atmosphere of the home. Throughout the spacious living room, you will find updated staircase railings, recessed lighting and a large window to allow plenty of sunlight, which is open to the eat-in kitchen.The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, with updated cabinetry, and an island. On the second floor you will find a luxurious, spa-like four-piece bath and three bedrooms with updated flooring. The lower level of the house has a fully finished basement, washer/dryer, access to the garage, as well as direct access to the back of the home where you will find the driveway. SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!!!
